957
01:25:23,439 --> 01:25:24,720
[SPEAKER_00] Jer bih mogao izgubiti toliko novca.

958
01:25:24,800 --> 01:25:29,520
[SPEAKER_00] Ali na kraju dana, to je tako jeftino da to nije velika stvar.

959
01:25:30,399 --> 01:25:34,800
