01:25:35,199 --> 01:25:35,279
[SPEAKER_01] godine?

961
01:25:35,600 --> 01:25:36,720
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, to je bilo 2018.

962
01:25:36,880 --> 01:25:36,960
[SPEAKER_01] godine.

963
01:25:37,119 --> 01:25:37,199
