[SPEAKER_00] zaraditi dovoljno da živim od toga.

978
01:26:41,439 --> 01:26:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo 2018.

979
01:26:42,399 --> 01:26:42,479
[SPEAKER_00] godine.

980
01:26:42,560 --> 01:26:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] To je bilo u jesen 2018.

981
01:26:45,119 --> 01:26:45,199
[SPEAKER_00] godine.

982
01:26:45,680 --> 01:26:46,960
[SPEAKER_00] I znate, još sam ovdje.

983
01:26:47,439 --> 01:26:48,640
