1033
01:31:34,880 --> 01:31:36,880
[SPEAKER_00] I tako mi je ponudio ovaj sadržaj.

1034
01:31:37,119 --> 01:31:37,760
[SPEAKER_00] Mi imamo udio prihoda.

1035
01:31:37,920 --> 01:31:40,800
